      • WORM_LENGTH

        public static final long WORM_LENGTH
        A value between 1 and 99999 should be used. Higher values will cause worms to be longer on average.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • WORM_RADIUS_CHANGE_RATE

        public static final int WORM_RADIUS_CHANGE_RATE
        The rate at which the worm's radius changes. Should be between 1 and 99. Low values cause the worm to rapidly change its radius, and higher values cause it to keep the same radius for a while.
        See Also:
